snippet: As both parties put more emphasis on winning the Hispanic demographic, the Latino Victory Project, a left-leaning group looking to animate voters and bring new leaders, will host its first major conference in Washington on Monday.

headline.main: Hispanic Group Brings New Voice in Washington to Coveted Demographic
